# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-02 11:43

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:7
translate portuguese day0_2a8ebe20:

    # "It has been a few days since I've' checked my e-mail."
    "Já passaram alguns dias desde que verifiquei o meu e-mail."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:10
translate portuguese day0_6ea4ba89:

    # "As soon as I see the message sitting in my inbox, I feel in my gut that something is wrong."
    "Assim que vejo a mensagem na minha caixa de entrada, sinto no meu íntimo que algo está errado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:14
translate portuguese day0_9bd314a2:

    # "Dad is missing? Disappeared? What does that even mean?"
    "O pai está desaparecido? Desapareceu? O que é que isso significa?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:15
translate portuguese day0_79ff2c19:

    # "I try to call Lisa, but the phone is disconnected. I e-mail back, but don't get a reply."
    "Tento ligar à Lisa, mas o telefone está desligado. Respondo por e-mail, mas não recebo resposta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:16
translate portuguese day0_af17984d:

    # "I need to go home."
    "Preciso de ir para casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:25
translate portuguese day0_a3b78350:

    # "TWO DAYS LATER"
    "DOIS DIAS DEPOIS"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:28
translate portuguese day0_030e178d:

    # "The Uber driver pulls up in front of my family's house – the house I had grown up in."
    "O motorista do Uber pára em frente à casa da minha família – a casa onde cresci."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:29
translate portuguese day0_949b7226:

    # "I've only been away for three years, but it feels like a lifetime. I barely remember the place, and the things I do remember feel like they had happened to somebody else – like I had dreamed them or seen them in a movie."
    "Só estive fora durante três anos, mas parece que foi uma eternidade. Mal me lembro do lugar, e as coisas de que me lembro parecem ter acontecido a outra pessoa – como se as tivesse sonhado ou visto num filme."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:32
translate portuguese day0_c142ebfa:

    # "After Mom died, my dad had moved us into this house. It was ten years later that he started dating Lisa and she moved in with us, along with her daughter Suzy."
    "Depois da morte da minha mãe, o meu pai mudou-nos para esta casa. Dez anos depois, ele começou a namorar com a Lisa e ela veio viver connosco, juntamente com a filha, a Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:33
translate portuguese day0_4b89f1ac:

    # "Then I moved away a year after that to go to college in Brazil – as far away from this place as I could possibly get."
    "Um ano depois, mudei-me para ir para a faculdade no Brasil – o mais longe possível deste lugar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:34
translate portuguese day0_5d54d54c:

    # "I didn't leave under the best circumstances either."
    "Também não parti nas melhores circunstâncias."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:35
translate portuguese day0_8f36008b:

    # "It felt like Dad was trying to replace Mom. I know now that I had been acting ridiculous, but I'd said some things that I regret, and I still haven't apologized for it."
    "Parecia que o pai estava a tentar substituir a mãe. Agora sei que me tinha comportado de forma ridícula, mas disse algumas coisas das quais me arrependo e ainda não pedi desculpa por isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:36
translate portuguese day0_dcd0e6e9:

    # "And now my dad is missing, and I may never be able to apologize to him."
    "E agora o meu pai está desaparecido e talvez nunca consiga pedir-lhe desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:37
translate portuguese day0_e04098c7:

    # "I need to know what's going on. Step one of that is talking to Lisa."
    "Preciso de saber o que se passa. O primeiro passo é falar com a Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:38
translate portuguese day0_ae22b1fe:

    # pc "Thanks for the ride."
    pc "Obrigado pela boleia."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:39
translate portuguese day0_6b2c2e0d:

    # "Uber Driver" "No problem. Good luck with your dad."
    "Uber Driver" "Não há problema. Boa sorte com o teu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:42
translate portuguese day0_bd06bca7:

    # "I step out of the car, pulling my suitcase behind me – all of my possessions hastily stuffed inside before leaving college and coming home."
    "Saio do carro, arrastando a minha mala atrás de mim – todos os meus pertences enfiados à pressa lá dentro antes de sair da faculdade e voltar para casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:43
translate portuguese day0_ee16e2af:

    # "The Uber Driver gives me a wave before driving away, leaving me standing in the driveway alone."
    "O motorista do Uber acena-me antes de se afastar, deixando-me sozinha na entrada."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:44
translate portuguese day0_1d05517b:

    # "The curtain in the front room moves to the side and a shadowed face looks out at me through the dusty glass."
    "A cortina da sala da frente move-se para o lado e um rosto na sombra olha para mim através do vidro empoeirado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:45
translate portuguese day0_ffa819f6:

    # "A moment later, the front door opens with a creak."
    "Um momento depois, a porta da frente abre-se com um rangido."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:49
translate portuguese day0_b886cbad:

    # sp "[pcname]?"
    sp "[pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:50
translate portuguese day0_1dce07cb:

    # pc "Hey Lisa."
    pc "Olá, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:51
translate portuguese day0_c451ce54:

    # sp "Oh my God, I can't believe you're here."
    sp "Meu Deus, não acredito que estás aqui."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:54
translate portuguese day0_4794e2ea:

    # "She rushes out of the house and across the lawn towards me, throwing her arms around my back and pulling me into a hug, sobbing lightly against my shoulder."
    "Ela sai a correr de casa e atravessa o relvado na minha direção, lançando-me os braços à volta das costas e puxando-me para um abraço, soluçando levemente contra o meu ombro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:55
translate portuguese day0_168a1c2d:

    # "Then she pulls away, tears still in her eyes."
    "Depois afasta-se, ainda com lágrimas nos olhos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:59
translate portuguese day0_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_sorry3.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:60
translate portuguese day0_b4977ec9:

    # sp "I'm sorry, it's just so good to see you again."
    sp "Desculpa, é que é tão bom ver-te outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:61
translate portuguese day0_ef7640f1:

    # sp "I didn't know if you got my e-mail or not."
    sp "Não sabia se tinhas recebido o meu e-mail ou não."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:62
translate portuguese day0_c351ff73:

    # pc "I tried to call you and message you back, but couldn't get through."
    pc "Tentei ligar-te e responder-te, mas não consegui contactar-te."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:63
translate portuguese day0_ab5c6be7:

    # sp "I didn't have enough money to keep paying the phone bill, or the internet. I used Suzy's phone to send that message."
    sp "Não tinha dinheiro suficiente para continuar a pagar a conta do telefone, nem da Internet. Usei o telemóvel da Suzy para enviar aquela mensagem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:64
translate portuguese day0_4aaf53f0:

    # sp "Why don't you come inside? Your room is still just like you left it. "
    sp "Porque não entras? O teu quarto continua tal e qual como o deixaste. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:65
translate portuguese day0_63023601:

    # pc "Okay."
    pc "Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:68
translate portuguese day0_f0440310:

    # "I look up at the house one more time, hesitating for some reason. "
    "Olho para a casa mais uma vez, hesitante por alguma razão. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:69
translate portuguese day0_c19f0382:

    # "Everything feels so awkward. Like seeing an old friend that you hadn't talked to since high school after you had both grown up and gone in completely different directions, became different people."
    "Tudo parece tão estranho. Como ver uma velha amiga com quem não falavas desde o liceu, depois de ambas terem crescido e seguido caminhos completamente diferentes, tendo-se tornado pessoas diferentes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:70
translate portuguese day0_521dbb9a:

    # "Lisa waits at the door expectantly."
    "A Lisa espera à porta, ansiosa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:73
translate portuguese day0_44deb548:

    # sp "Come on."
    sp "Anda lá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:74
translate portuguese day0_7ef33df2:

    # "I follow her inside."
    "Sigo-a para dentro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:78
translate portuguese day0_cb8b4dc4:

    # "The house isn't much different than I remembered. Some new decorations, but a lot of the old stuff is still there too."
    "A casa não está muito diferente do que eu me lembrava. Algumas decorações novas, mas muitas das coisas antigas também ainda estão lá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:80
translate portuguese day0_f76dd47c:

    # "A doorway to the right leads to the kitchen, with the always-clean white cabinets and wooden countertops."
    "Uma porta à direita leva à cozinha, com os armários brancos sempre limpos e as bancadas de madeira."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:83
translate portuguese day0_5f5c5eda:

    # "To the left, another doorway goes into the living room, where there are a couple of sofas and a television mounted on the wall across from them."
    "À esquerda, outra porta dá para a sala de estar, onde há dois sofás e uma televisão montada na parede em frente a eles."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:84
translate portuguese day0_7532ecd1:

    # "The furniture is different, the television upgraded, but the photos on the wall are exactly the same as I remember them three years ago."
    "A mobília está diferente, a televisão foi atualizada, mas as fotos na parede são exatamente as mesmas de que me lembro há três anos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:85
translate portuguese day0_62149b84:

    # "Pictures of me mostly, along with others of my dad and Lisa, a few of Suzy, and even some of my mom."
    "Fotografias minhas, na sua maioria, juntamente com outras do meu pai e da Lisa, algumas da Suzy e até algumas da minha mãe."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:89
translate portuguese day0_dcb39111:

    # "Directly in front of me are the stairs leading up to the second floor, while the hall going past the stairs leads to the door that goes down into the basement where Dad's office is."
    "Mesmo à minha frente estão as escadas que levam ao segundo andar, enquanto o corredor que passa pelas escadas conduz à porta que desce para a cave, onde fica o escritório do meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:90
translate portuguese day0_a1a128e4:

    # "There's police tape over the door. I'll have to ask Lisa about that."
    "Há fita policial sobre a porta. Vou ter de perguntar à Lisa sobre isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:91
translate portuguese day0_f27132b3:

    # "Past that, the door to the right goes to the master bedroom and bathroom and the door to the left leads to the laundry room. Then there's a patio door in the back that opens into the back yard."
    "Depois disso, a porta à direita dá para o quarto principal e a casa de banho e a porta à esquerda leva à lavandaria. Depois há uma porta de pátio nas traseiras que dá para o quintal."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:94
translate portuguese day0_1758423e:

    # pc "What's the deal with the police tape?"
    pc "O que se passa com a fita policial?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:95
translate portuguese day0_3089e2b3:

    # sp "Oh, they don't want anybody down there until they get finished going through some of the things that they took."
    sp "Ah, eles não querem que ninguém vá lá abaixo até terminarem de examinar algumas das coisas que levaram."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:96
translate portuguese day0_78bdaf37:

    # sp "The detective locked the door and took the key with her."
    sp "A detetive trancou a porta e levou a chave com ela."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:97
translate portuguese day0_c627e703:

    # pc "Wow. Okay."
    pc "Uau. Está bem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:98
translate portuguese day0_fec9a6b1:

    # sp "You can go put your bag in your room if you want. I was just finishing up dinner."
    sp "Podes ir colocar a tua mala no teu quarto, se quiseres. Eu estava a terminar o jantar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:99
translate portuguese day0_aef6c125:

    # pc "Oh, don't worry about it. I can just get take-out or something. I know you weren't really prepared for me coming today."
    pc "Ah, não te preocupes com isso. Posso pedir comida ou algo do género. Sei que não estavas realmente preparada para a minha chegada hoje."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:100
translate portuguese day0_c773dfdd:

    # sp "Nonsense. I made chicken fried steak. There's plenty."
    sp "Que disparate. Fiz bife frito com frango. Há bastante."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:101
translate portuguese day0_18768229:

    # "Chicken fried steak does sound delicious."
    "Bife de frango frito parece delicioso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:102
translate portuguese day0_05d61a38:

    # pc "Okay, I'll just go put these up."
    pc "Está bem, vou só arrumar isto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:105
translate portuguese day0_00910cb6:

    # sp "Sounds good. Make yourself comfortable. Suzy will be home soon. I'm sure she'll be excited to see you."
    sp "Parece-me bem. Fica à vontade. A Suzy chega a casa em breve. Tenho a certeza de que ela vai ficar entusiasmada por te ver."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:106
translate portuguese day0_54c86bd6:

    # "I doubt that. Suzy and I had never really gotten along. I think that she's always been jealous of me, because I'm older and always got to do more interesting things than she did."
    "Duvido. A Suzy e eu nunca nos demos muito bem. Acho que ela sempre teve inveja de mim, porque sou mais velha e sempre pude fazer coisas mais interessantes do que ela."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:107
translate portuguese day0_f84afb0d:

    # "She seems so stuck-up to me. Like she and Lisa are just so much better than me and Dad."
    "Ela parece-me tão presunçosa. Como se ela e a Lisa fossem muito melhores do que eu e o pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:108
translate portuguese day0_1fb90770:

    # "That was three years ago though, I had to remind myself. People can change. I know I have. Although returning to this place is making old feelings return as well."
    "Mas isso foi há três anos, tive de me lembrar. As pessoas podem mudar. Eu sei que mudei. Embora voltar a este lugar esteja a fazer com que os velhos sentimentos também regressem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:109
translate portuguese day0_d7c1e2c2:

    # "I need to try to give them a chance. To start over. I need to be nice. It would be good for me and for the entire family."
    "Preciso de tentar dar-lhes uma oportunidade. Para recomeçar. Preciso de ser simpática. Seria bom para mim e para toda a família."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:112
translate portuguese day0_6834d5ee:

    # "I take my bag up the stairs. My door is to the left, while Suzy's door, which she painted as soon as she moved into the house, is to the right."
    "Subo as escadas com a minha mala. A minha porta fica à esquerda, enquanto a porta da Suzy, que ela pintou assim que se mudou para a casa, fica à direita."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:113
translate portuguese day0_c3457fef:

    # "I open my bedroom door and walk inside."
    "Abro a porta do meu quarto e entro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:116
translate portuguese day0_e134735d:

    # "All my junk that had been lying around the room when I left is all put away now, but the decorations are exactly how I had left them."
    "Todas as minhas tralhas que estavam espalhadas pelo quarto quando parti estão agora arrumadas, mas as decorações estão exatamente como as deixei."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:117
translate portuguese day0_81daa922:

    # "Band, movie, and video game posters on the walls. My old laptop and computer desk are in the corner covered in a thin layer of dust."
    "Pôsteres de bandas, filmes e jogos de vídeo nas paredes. O meu velho portátil e a secretária do computador estão no canto, cobertos por uma fina camada de pó."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:118
translate portuguese day0_d3121b8d:

    # "My Queen-sized bed is in the other corner, made up as if it were waiting for me. My nightstand next to it still has my favorite lamp on it as well."
    "A minha cama queen-size está no outro canto, feita como se estivesse à minha espera. A minha mesinha de cabeceira ao lado ainda tem o meu candeeiro favorito em cima."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:119
translate portuguese day0_5c2ab389:

    # "I look around at the posters and can't help but laugh at myself. I had thought this stuff was so cool. I hadn't even realized how much I'd changed over the few years I'd been away from Skyhill."
    "Olho à minha volta para os pôsteres e não consigo deixar de rir de mim mesma. Eu achava que estas coisas eram tão fixes. Nem sequer me tinha apercebido do quanto tinha mudado nos poucos anos em que estive longe de Skyhill."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:120
translate portuguese day0_ef69d95d:

    # "I shake my head and put my bag on the dresser nearby that is still full of my clothes that I'd left behind when I moved."
    "Abano a cabeça e coloco a minha mala na cómoda ali ao lado, que ainda está cheia das roupas que deixei para trás quando me mudei."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:121
translate portuguese day0_31c8b952:

    # "I shuffle through some of the clothing before deciding that all this stuff is going to have to get donated. I won't be caught dead wearing these clothes again."
    "Reviro algumas das roupas antes de decidir que tudo isto vai ter de ser doado. Nem morta me apanhariam a usar estas roupas outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:122
translate portuguese day0_f0fd0cf7:

    # "If I'm going to stay here for any length of time, the decorations on the wall have to change too."
    "Se vou ficar aqui por algum tempo, a decoração na parede também tem de mudar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:123
translate portuguese day0_6548a872:

    # "I'm not into these bands at all anymore. Hell, most of them aren't together anymore and the lead singer in that one is in jail over sexual assault charges."
    "Já não gosto nada destas bandas. Bolas, a maioria delas já nem existe e o vocalista daquela está na prisão por acusações de agressão sexual."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:124
translate portuguese day0_f45d7436:

    # "I walk over to that poster and rip it down, ball it up, and toss it into the garbage can."
    "Dirijo-me àquele cartaz, arranco-o, amasso-o e atiro-o para o caixote do lixo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:125
translate portuguese day0_daf8f563:

    # pc "Screw it."
    pc "Que se lixe."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:126
translate portuguese day0_1153338c:

    # "I rip the rest of them down too. I need a new start. I'm not the same person that I had been when I lived here before and liked this stuff. I've changed and everything else needs to change too."
    "Arranquei os restantes também. Preciso de um novo começo. Não sou a mesma pessoa que era quando vivia aqui antes e gostava destas coisas. Mudei e tudo o resto também precisa de mudar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:129
translate portuguese day0_11cc59ea:

    # "When I've finished, a couple minutes later, the walls are bare and the trash can is full. I'll redecorate later, if I decide to stay."
    "Quando terminei, alguns minutos depois, as paredes estavam vazias e o caixote do lixo estava cheio. Vou redecorar mais tarde, se decidir ficar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:133
translate portuguese day0_c85d2e30:

    # "I take the bag out of the trash can and carry it down the stairs, heading towards the back door where I know the outdoor bins are kept."
    "Tiro o saco do caixote do lixo e levo-o pelas escadas abaixo, dirigindo-me para a porta das traseiras, onde sei que estão os contentores exteriores."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:134
translate portuguese day0_c7469e66:

    # "I'd done this same routine every week growing up. Taking out the garbage was always one of the chores that I did for my weekly $20 allowance."
    "Fazia esta mesma rotina todas as semanas enquanto crescia. Levar o lixo para fora era sempre uma das tarefas que fazia para ganhar a minha mesada semanal de 20 dólares."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:135
translate portuguese day0_b9ad02f6:

    # "Lisa calls from the kitchen as I pass."
    "A Lisa chama-me da cozinha quando passo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:136
translate portuguese day0_15b806ca:

    # sp "Where are you going? Not leaving already are you?"
    sp "Onde vais? Não vais embora já, pois não?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:137
translate portuguese day0_b5e60a63:

    # pc "Just taking out the garbage. I'll be right back."
    pc "Vou só deitar fora o lixo. Volto já."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:138
translate portuguese day0_c85b3c7e:

    # "I walk past the basement door, past the door leading into my dad's and Lisa's room, and out the back door."
    "Passo pela porta da cave, passo pela porta que dá para o quarto do meu pai e da Lisa e saio pela porta das traseiras."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:141
translate portuguese day0_f2d37ac4:

    # "The back yard is a mess. One of the fence pickets is down, there are patches of weeds everywhere, and the grass is up past my knees, as if nobody has mowed it in months."
    "O quintal está uma confusão. Uma das estacas da vedação está caída, há manchas de ervas daninhas por todo o lado e a relva chega-me acima dos joelhos, como se ninguém a cortasse há meses."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:142
translate portuguese day0_f94bb3ce:

    # "I walk around to where the trashcans are, behind the garage. They're overflowing with garbage as if somebody had forgotten to take them out to the curb last week... and maybe the week before that as well."
    "Caminho até ao local onde estão os caixotes do lixo, atrás da garagem. Estão a transbordar de lixo, como se alguém se tivesse esquecido de os levar para o passeio na semana passada... e talvez na semana anterior também."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:143
translate portuguese day0_12d3e32e:

    # "I sit the trash bag on top of the bin, making a mental note to ask when trash pick-up is, so that I can be sure to get it out. "
    "Coloco o saco do lixo em cima da lixeira, fazendo uma nota mental para perguntar quando é a recolha do lixo, para ter a certeza de que o vou colocar lá fora. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:144
translate portuguese day0_734ac1ca:

    # "I guess Lisa has been a bit distracted with my missing dad."
    "Acho que a Lisa tem estado um pouco distraída com o desaparecimento do meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:145
translate portuguese day0_0a4deb90:

    # "???" "[pcname]? Is that you?"
    "???" "[pcname]? És tu?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:150
translate portuguese day0_13302e89:

    # "I look over to where the voice came from and see a face watching me through the gap in the wooden fence on the other side of the yard."
    "Olho para onde veio a voz e vejo um rosto a observar-me através da abertura na cerca de madeira do outro lado do quintal."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:151
translate portuguese day0_82512aa5:

    # pc "Jamie?"
    pc "Jamie?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:152
translate portuguese day0_c324c938:

    # "Jamie had been my neighbor for years growing up. We played together in the yard when we were young and were good friends all the way through junior high."
    "A Jamie foi minha vizinha durante anos enquanto crescíamos. Brincávamos juntas no quintal quando éramos pequenas e fomos boas amigas durante todo o ensino básico."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:153
translate portuguese day0_66d7d185:

    # "Then we started hanging out with different crowds when we went to high school and never really kept up with each other after that, aside from nods as we passed in the hall."
    "Depois, começámos a andar com grupos diferentes quando fomos para o liceu e nunca mais nos mantivemos em contacto depois disso, além de acenos de cabeça quando nos cruzávamos no corredor."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:154
translate portuguese day0_d75b5d1b:

    # "I walk through the overgrown grass to the fence to talk to her."
    "Atravesso a relva alta até à cerca para falar com ela."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:158
translate portuguese day0_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice "voices/jamie_001.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_001.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:159
translate portuguese day0_c579b7b0:

    # gnd "I'm surprised you remembered my name."
    gnd "Estou surpreendida por te lembrares do meu nome."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:160
translate portuguese day0_59b86f08:

    # pc "We were friends for years, Jamie! I'm not going to forget your name. How have you been?"
    pc "Fomos amigos durante anos, Jamie! Não vou esquecer o teu nome. Como tens passado?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:163
translate portuguese day0_21d6813b:

    # gnd "Oh, pretty good. You know, just going to college and still living here."
    gnd "Oh, muito bem. Sabes, ando na faculdade e continuo a viver aqui."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:164
translate portuguese day0_975b1fd3:

    # gnd "What about you? I thought you were going to school in Brazil or something?"
    gnd "E tu? Pensei que fosses estudar no Brasil ou algo do género?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:165
translate portuguese day0_a95318dd:

    # pc "I was. I finished my third year there and was planning on staying to graduate, but this stuff with my dad happened."
    pc "Eu ia. Terminei o terceiro ano lá e estava a planear ficar para me formar, mas aconteceu aquela coisa com o meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:168
translate portuguese day0_e16cc8f9:

    # gnd "Oh yeah, I heard about that. They still don't know what happened to him?"
    gnd "Ah, sim, ouvi falar disso. Ainda não sabem o que lhe aconteceu?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:169
translate portuguese day0_35917d41:

    # pc "I don't think so. I just got here and haven't really started looking into it. Trying to settle in first, you know?"
    pc "Acho que não. Acabei de chegar e ainda não comecei a investigar. Estou a tentar instalar-me primeiro, sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:170
translate portuguese day0_58eca7fc:

    # gnd "I understand."
    gnd "Compreendo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:171
translate portuguese day0_78191689:

    # "We stand there for a moment in awkward silence. It's hard to have a normal conversation with the cloud of my missing father looming over our heads."
    "Ficamos ali por um momento num silêncio constrangedor. É difícil ter uma conversa normal com a nuvem do meu pai desaparecido a pairar sobre as nossas cabeças."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:174
translate portuguese day0_8fa47015:

    # gnd "We should go grab a coffee sometime and catch up."
    gnd "Devíamos ir tomar um café um dia destes e pôr a conversa em dia."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:182
translate portuguese neighborsure_eb2314d3:

    # pc "Sure, I'd like that."
    pc "Claro, adoraria."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:186
translate portuguese neighborsure_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_002.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:187
translate portuguese neighborsure_59e12605:

    # gnd "Great! I'm looking forward to it."
    gnd "Ótimo! Estou ansioso por isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:188
translate portuguese neighborsure_616126a9:

    # gnd "Let me give you my phone number."
    gnd "Deixa-me dar-te o meu número de telefone."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:189
translate portuguese neighborsure_ec3ea59f:

    # pc "Well, I don't have a phone right now. I sort of left in a hurry and forgot the thing in Brazil. I even had to call an Uber from a pay phone."
    pc "Bem, não tenho telemóvel neste momento. Saí à pressa e esqueci-o no Brasil. Até tive de chamar um Uber de um telefone público."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:190
translate portuguese neighborsure_4d9a5c08:

    # gnd "Wow, I didn't even know you could do that."
    gnd "Uau, nem sabia que se podia fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:191
translate portuguese neighborsure_07ae5ff4:

    # gnd "Well, you know where I live anyways. Just come over and see me sometime."
    gnd "Bem, de qualquer forma, sabes onde moro. Aparece para me visitar um dia destes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:192
translate portuguese neighborsure_bf344fc1:

    # pc "I'll be sure to do that."
    pc "Vou fazer isso com certeza."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:193
translate portuguese neighborsure_3ea1fb42:

    # gnd "Okay, I'll let you get back to what you were doing. It's really good to see you again, [pcname]."
    gnd "Ok, vou deixar-te voltar ao que estavas a fazer. É muito bom ver-te de novo, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:194
translate portuguese neighborsure_b59564bf:

    # pc "Good to see you too. Talk to you later."
    pc "Também é bom ver-te. Falamos mais tarde."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:195
translate portuguese neighborsure_53dafd04:

    # "She smiles and gives me a wave before turning around and walking back inside her house."
    "Ela sorri e acena-me antes de se virar e voltar para dentro de casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:200
translate portuguese neighborbusy_af2bb653:

    # "She is unable to hide the disappointment on her face."
    "Ela não consegue esconder a desilusão no rosto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:202
translate portuguese neighborbusy_d41d8cd9:

    # voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"
    voice "voices/jamie_003.mp3"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:203
translate portuguese neighborbusy_34e40ec9:

    # gnd "Oh, okay."
    gnd "Ah, está bem."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:204
translate portuguese neighborbusy_1708b5ad:

    # gnd "Well, if you change your mind, you know where I live."
    gnd "Bem, se mudares de ideias, sabes onde moro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:205
translate portuguese neighborbusy_994698a4:

    # gnd "I'll let you get back to what you were doing. It was nice to see you again."
    gnd "Vou deixar-te voltar ao que estavas a fazer. Foi bom ver-te novamente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:208
translate portuguese neighborbusy_4d48c356:

    # "She puts on an obviously fake smile and gives me a short wave before quickly turning around and walking back inside her house."
    "Ela faz um sorriso obviamente falso e acena-me brevemente antes de se virar rapidamente e voltar para dentro de casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:215
translate portuguese dinner_6bf7ca74:

    # "I hear a car pull into the driveway and the door shut. Must be Suzy."
    "Ouço um carro a entrar na entrada e a porta a fechar-se. Deve ser a Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:216
translate portuguese dinner_15d46ed4:

    # "It's a bit strange to think of her driving. She'd been fifteen years old when I left and most of the time I had to drive her everywhere."
    "É um pouco estranho pensar nela a conduzir. Ela tinha quinze anos quando eu parti e, na maior parte das vezes, era eu que tinha de a levar a todo o lado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:217
translate portuguese dinner_0530e225:

    # "Now, I might need her to drive me. Until I can get a car at least. How the hell am I going to get a car?"
    "Agora, talvez precise que ela me leve. Pelo menos até conseguir arranjar um carro. Como raio é que vou arranjar um carro?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:223
translate portuguese dinner_a0b77eb0:

    # "I walk back inside and see Lisa and Suzy standing at the front door. Suzy looks over at me with an expression that I can't decipher."
    "Volto para dentro e vejo a Lisa e a Suzy à porta da frente. A Suzy olha para mim com uma expressão que não consigo decifrar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:224
translate portuguese dinner_536ca09a:

    # "Is she happy to see me, or upset, or just surprised?"
    "Ela está feliz por me ver, chateada ou apenas surpreendida?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:225
translate portuguese dinner_b9a34438:

    # "She looks a lot different than the last time I had seen her. Not a child anymore. All grown up."
    "Ela parece muito diferente da última vez que a vi. Já não é uma criança. Está toda crescida."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:249
translate portuguese dinner_b9085ed0:

    # sp "There he is now."
    sp "Aí está ele."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:250
translate portuguese dinner_f3bfb9f9:

    # pc "Hey, [sis]."
    pc "Olá, [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:254
translate portuguese dinner_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_hey1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_hey1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:255
translate portuguese dinner_f4685411:

    # ss "Hey."
    ss "Olá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:258
translate portuguese dinner_266752d5:

    # "She turns back towards Lisa."
    "Ela vira-se de novo para a Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:259
translate portuguese dinner_099bdf34:

    # ss "So what's for dinner?"
    ss "Então, o que há para o jantar?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:262
translate portuguese dinner_6adaf09c:

    # sp "That's it? Hey, what's for dinner?"
    sp "É só isso? Ei, o que há para o jantar?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:263
translate portuguese dinner_d377dbd3:

    # sp "You haven't seen [pcname] in three years. At least give him a hug or something."
    sp "Não vês o [pcname] há três anos. Pelo menos dá-lhe um abraço ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:266
translate portuguese dinner_7d526f5b:

    # ss "Do you want a hug, [bro]?"
    ss "Queres um abraço, [bro]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:273
translate portuguese hugno_1843469a:

    # pc "I mean you don't have to."
    pc "Quero dizer, não tens de o fazer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:275
translate portuguese hugno_67e29172:

    # ss "Good. I smell dinner. Let's eat, I'm starving!"
    ss "Ótimo. Sinto o cheiro do jantar. Vamos comer, estou esfomeado!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:279
translate portuguese hugno_73d3290c:

    # sp "Suzy!"
    sp "Suzy!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:280
translate portuguese hugno_6f0bb30f:

    # ss "He said I don't have to. Not everybody is a hugger mom. Respect people's boundaries."
    ss "Ele disse que não tenho de o fazer. Nem toda a gente é do tipo de dar abraços, mãe. Respeita os limites das pessoas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:281
translate portuguese hugno_672d419d:

    # sp "I can't believe you."
    sp "Não acredito nisto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:284
translate portuguese hugyes_0fdda645:

    # pc "We probably should, right?"
    pc "Provavelmente devíamos, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:287
translate portuguese hugyes_b52b7bc9:

    # ss "I guess."
    ss "Acho que sim."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:291
translate portuguese hugyes_627ce8ab:

    # "She hesitantly walks towards me and lightly puts her arms around me, barely touching."
    "Ela caminha hesitante na minha direção e coloca os braços à minha volta, mal me tocando."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:292
translate portuguese hugyes_e1fa87a8:

    # pc "It's good to see you, [sis]."
    pc "É bom ver-te, [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:293
translate portuguese hugyes_3caba330:

    # ss "Good to see you too."
    ss "Também é bom ver-te."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:294
translate portuguese hugyes_a2f7fa6a:

    # "Then she quickly pulls away."
    "Depois, ela afasta-se rapidamente."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:300
translate portuguese hugyes_78d5d1d8:

    # ss "Alright, we hugged, let's eat, I'm starving!"
    ss "Pronto, já nos abraçámos, vamos comer, estou esfomeada!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:305
translate portuguese dinner2_4f4f66ba:

    # "We make our plates in the kitchen and bring them to the small four-person table in the dining room."
    "Arrumamos os pratos na cozinha e levamo-los para a pequena mesa de quatro pessoas na sala de jantar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:306
translate portuguese dinner2_a501017d:

    # "Lisa had made chicken fried steak and mashed potatoes with gravy, along with creamed spinach and dinner rolls."
    "A Lisa tinha feito bife de frango frito e puré de batata com molho, juntamente com espinafres com natas e pãezinhos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:307
translate portuguese dinner2_a4109bc0:

    # "I'm not a big fan of spinach, but everything else looks delicious."
    "Não sou grande fã de espinafres, mas tudo o resto parece delicioso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:308
translate portuguese dinner2_82b4d135:

    # ss "Thanks for cooking Mom. This is amazing!"
    ss "Obrigado por cozinhares, mãe. Isto está incrível!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:309
translate portuguese dinner2_132b8415:

    # sp "Amazing might be a strong word. [pcname] has been down in Brazil for the last three years. I bet they have some real amazing food down there, right?"
    sp "Incrível talvez seja uma palavra forte. A [pcname] tem estado no Brasil nos últimos três anos. Aposto que lá têm comida verdadeiramente incrível, certo?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:316
translate portuguese amazingtacos_d1df5759:

    # pc "No, she's right. These are perfect."
    pc "Não, ela tem razão. Estes estão perfeitos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:317
translate portuguese amazingtacos_ac97708c:

    # pc "The food in Brazil was great, but there's something about a good homemade chicken fried steak that makes it really feel like I'm home again."
    pc "A comida no Brasil era ótima, mas há algo num bom bife frito caseiro que me faz sentir mesmo em casa outra vez."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:320
translate portuguese amazingtacos_b2a06636:

    # sp "I'm glad you like it, and I'm glad that you're home."
    sp "Ainda bem que gostas e ainda bem que estás em casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:323
translate portuguese mehtacos_bbafcb97:

    # pc "Yeah, this is nowhere near as good as the empanadas down there."
    pc "Pois, isto não chega nem perto das empanadas de lá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:326
translate portuguese mehtacos_984cd73b:

    # sp "See, this is just cheap steak, breaded and fried. Not exactly gourmet cooking."
    sp "Vês, isto é só um bife barato, panado e frito. Não é propriamente cozinha gourmet."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:327
translate portuguese mehtacos_b89e34ff:

    # "Suzy glared at me and shook her head."
    "A Suzy lançou-me um olhar fulminante e abanou a cabeça."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:332
translate portuguese dinner3_e9cd228e:

    # ss "So why are you back anyways?"
    ss "Então, porque é que voltaste, afinal?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:335
translate portuguese dinner3_900dc08e:

    # sp "Be nice."
    sp "Sê simpática."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:336
translate portuguese dinner3_ed0bffd1:

    # ss "I am being nice. It's just a question."
    ss "Estou a ser simpática. É só uma pergunta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:337
translate portuguese dinner3_d0083d8d:

    # pc "I came back to help find my dad."
    pc "Voltei para ajudar a encontrar o meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:338
translate portuguese dinner3_92f7529c:

    # ss "Well good luck with that. He ran off with another woman. If he wanted to be found, we would've already found him."
    ss "Bem, boa sorte com isso. Ele fugiu com outra mulher. Se ele quisesse ser encontrado, já o teríamos encontrado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:341
translate portuguese dinner3_06a83c9b:

    # sp "Stop."
    sp "Pára."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:342
translate portuguese dinner3_447f8572:

    # sp "Don't talk about him like that. Just stop."
    sp "Não fales dele assim. Pára com isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:343
translate portuguese dinner3_95ae9b92:

    # ss "Sorry Mom."
    ss "Desculpa, mãe."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:346
translate portuguese dinner3_d95dc3cd:

    # sp "I don't want to argue at the table. Let's just have a nice dinner and we can talk about your father tomorrow."
    sp "Não quero discutir à mesa. Vamos apenas ter um jantar agradável e podemos falar sobre o teu pai amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:347
translate portuguese dinner3_74555258:

    # "We sit in silence for a few minutes, eating, not saying anything. "
    "Ficamos sentados em silêncio por alguns minutos, a comer, sem dizer nada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:348
translate portuguese dinner3_9ecbea22:

    # "I want to ask more. I want to know why she thought my dad would have run off with another woman. But Lisa is obviously upset, and I don't want to start a fight. "
    "Quero perguntar mais. Quero saber por que razão ela achou que o meu pai teria fugido com outra mulher. Mas a Lisa está obviamente chateada, e não quero começar uma discussão. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:351
translate portuguese dinner3_f1c7cb27:

    # sp "How long are you planning on staying, [pcname]?"
    sp "Quanto tempo pretendes ficar, [pcname]?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:352
translate portuguese dinner3_ab1f2008:

    # pc "I'm back permanently. "
    pc "Voltei para ficar. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:353
translate portuguese dinner3_2441805f:

    # sp "What? You're not going back to school? "
    sp "O quê? Não vais voltar para a escola? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:354
translate portuguese dinner3_4f22cfa1:

    # pc "I can't. The scholarship was for four years, but if I miss any time, the scholarship is revoked. School started two days ago. I won't be able to go back. "
    pc "Não posso. A bolsa era para quatro anos, mas se eu faltar algum tempo, a bolsa é revogada. As aulas começaram há dois dias. Não vou conseguir voltar. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:356
translate portuguese dinner3_eb965744:

    # sp "Oh no! I wouldn't have wanted you to come if I'd known that! Your father wouldn't have wanted you to give up school to help find him either!"
    sp "Oh, não! Eu não teria querido que viesses se soubesse disso! O teu pai também não teria querido que desistisses da escola para ajudar a encontrá-lo!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:357
translate portuguese dinner3_3c14b8e8:

    # pc "It's done. I wanted to come back. I wasn't doing great at school anyways. I'm not sure I would've made it through the next year. "
    pc "Já está feito. Eu queria voltar. De qualquer forma, não estava a ir muito bem na escola. Não tenho a certeza se teria conseguido passar o próximo ano. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:358
translate portuguese dinner3_f36256a6:

    # sp "So what are you going to do then? "
    sp "Então, o que vais fazer agora? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:359
translate portuguese dinner3_e26eb0c6:

    # pc "I'll go to school here. Finish up my degree and get a job here. That way I can help you out and try to find my dad. "
    pc "Vou estudar aqui. Terminar a minha licenciatura e arranjar um emprego aqui. Assim, posso ajudar-te e tentar encontrar o meu pai. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:360
translate portuguese dinner3_f98fa327:

    # "Lisa looks like she is about to cry. "
    "A Lisa parece estar prestes a chorar. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:362
translate portuguese dinner3_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_sorry2.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_sorry2.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:363
translate portuguese dinner3_ce872a9f:

    # sp "I'm sorry you had to give all that up. I shouldn't have even sent that e-mail. "
    sp "Lamento que tenhas tido de desistir de tudo isso. Nem devia ter enviado aquele e-mail. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:364
translate portuguese dinner3_f416188f:

    # pc "It's fine, really. I'm glad you sent it. I want to help, and I like being back. I didn't really have any friends down there. It's hard when you can barely speak the language. "
    pc "Não faz mal, a sério. Ainda bem que o enviaste. Quero ajudar e gosto de estar de volta. Na verdade, não tinha amigos lá. É difícil quando mal se consegue falar a língua. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:365
translate portuguese dinner3_e31cfdde:

    # pc "And I missed my family. "
    pc "E sentia saudades da minha família. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:367
translate portuguese dinner3_5f7f342a:

    # sp "We missed you too, right Suzy?"
    sp "Também sentíamos saudades tuas, certo, Suzy?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:369
translate portuguese dinner3_48c93c5d:

    # ss "Gag me. "
    ss "Que nojo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:370
translate portuguese dinner3_081c7332:

    # ss "If you're going to sign up for school, you better do it tomorrow. Registration is closing soon. "
    ss "Se vais inscrever-te na escola, é melhor fazê-lo amanhã. As inscrições fecham em breve. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:371
translate portuguese dinner3_038c9ed9:

    # sp "She's right. Suzy, you can give him a ride up to the school in the morning so he can get everything straightened out. "
    sp "Ela tem razão. Suzy, podes dar-lhe boleia até à escola de manhã para que ele possa tratar de tudo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:373
translate portuguese dinner3_c0cf4e1c:

    # ss "Why do I have to give him a ride? "
    ss "Porque é que tenho de lhe dar boleia? "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:374
translate portuguese dinner3_31d1c1eb:

    # sp "Because I have to work and [pcname] just got back to town and doesn't have a car."
    sp "Porque eu tenho de trabalhar e [pcname] acabou de voltar à cidade e não tem carro."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:375
translate portuguese dinner3_c6d0a215:

    # sp "AND because I asked you to. "
    sp "E porque te pedi. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:377
translate portuguese dinner3_7197e500:

    # ss "Okay, fine. Be ready to go at 10 a.m. though. If you're not ready, I'm not taking you. "
    ss "Está bem, tudo bem. Mas está pronta para sair às 10 da manhã. Se não estiveres pronta, não te levo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:378
translate portuguese dinner3_b0883318:

    # sp "Show him around town too. It's been a while since he's been here."
    sp "Mostra-lhe a cidade também. Já faz algum tempo que ele não vem cá."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:379
translate portuguese dinner3_a6b45ae3:

    # ss "Fine, but you need to get a car fast, because I can't be your chauffeur all the time. I have a life, you know."
    ss "Tudo bem, mas tens de arranjar um carro depressa, porque não posso ser a tua motorista o tempo todo. Tenho uma vida, sabes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:380
translate portuguese dinner3_9083962a:

    # pc "You're right. I need to get a car. I need a cell phone too. So I need a job."
    pc "Tens razão. Preciso de arranjar um carro. Também preciso de um telemóvel. Por isso, preciso de um emprego."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:382
translate portuguese dinner3_4bee5430:

    # sp "What happened to your cell phone?"
    sp "O que aconteceu ao teu telemóvel?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:383
translate portuguese dinner3_0e7d850c:

    # pc "I sort of forgot it in Brazil."
    pc "Esqueci-mo no Brasil."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:384
translate portuguese dinner3_fcf63dc9:

    # sp "Oh no!"
    sp "Oh não!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:385
translate portuguese dinner3_706f59f6:

    # pc "No big deal. I'll get another, but I need money for that."
    pc "Não faz mal. Arranjo outro, mas preciso de dinheiro para isso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:386
translate portuguese dinner3_fe6322c5:

    # sp "It seems they're always looking for administrative assistants at the law offices downtown. I'm sure you could do that, with how smart you are. "
    sp "Parece que estão sempre à procura de assistentes administrativos nos escritórios de advogados no centro. Tenho a certeza de que te daria jeito, com a inteligência que tens. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:388
translate portuguese dinner3_b7e8d5cc:

    # ss "Who says he's so smart?"
    ss "Quem é que diz que ele é tão inteligente?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:389
translate portuguese dinner3_905e17eb:

    # sp "He qualified for that college in Brazil on a full scholarship. "
    sp "Ele foi admitido naquela faculdade no Brasil com uma bolsa integral. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:390
translate portuguese dinner3_1232931d:

    # ss "Yeah, and then flunked out of it apparently. "
    ss "Sim, e depois foi reprovado, ao que parece. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:392
translate portuguese dinner3_9a859b5f:

    # sp "Be nice! "
    sp "Sê simpática! "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:393
translate portuguese dinner3_eac3f948:

    # "Suzy rolls her eyes. "
    "A Suzy revira os olhos. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:395
translate portuguese dinner3_cd1c0018:

    # sp "Anyway, I was going to say, you could use your father's car, if we could find the key."
    sp "De qualquer forma, eu ia dizer que podias usar o carro do teu pai, se conseguíssemos encontrar a chave."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:396
translate portuguese dinner3_fb35da6b:

    # sp "I'm not sure where he put it. I couldn't find it in his dresser and I didn't touch much down in the basement before the police locked it up."
    sp "Não sei bem onde ele a colocou. Não a encontrei na cómoda dele e não mexi muito na cave antes de a polícia a ter fechado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:397
translate portuguese dinner3_602ba288:

    # sp "I haven't even seen him drive it in at least a month."
    sp "Já nem o vejo a conduzi-lo há pelo menos um mês."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:398
translate portuguese dinner3_3c301d5a:

    # pc "Okay, I'll check it out sometime."
    pc "Está bem, vou dar uma olhadela noutro momento."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:401
translate portuguese dinner3_3dbf05d8:

    # ss "I'm done. I'm going up to my room."
    ss "Já terminei. Vou para o meu quarto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:402
translate portuguese dinner3_f3968cc8:

    # ss "Be ready at 10 tomorrow [bro]."
    ss "Esteja pronta às 10 amanhã [bro]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:403
translate portuguese dinner3_0da1b457:

    # "With that she rushes out of the dining room and up the stairs. "
    "Dito isto, ela sai a correr da sala de jantar e sobe as escadas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:406
translate portuguese dinner3_e9cab60e:

    # sp "You'll have to excuse her. She's probably just going to talk to her boyfriend."
    sp "Tem de a desculpar. Provavelmente vai apenas falar com o namorado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:407
translate portuguese dinner3_3a98b7ff:

    # sp "She does this almost every night. He lives in Whiterock and they hardly ever get to see each other anymore, so they talk on the phone a lot. "
    sp "Ela faz isto quase todas as noites. Ele mora em Whiterock e já quase não se conseguem ver, por isso falam muito ao telefone. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:408
translate portuguese dinner3_c969083e:

    # sp "Try to get along with her, okay?"
    sp "Tenta dar-te bem com ela, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:409
translate portuguese dinner3_cfc6d9f8:

    # sp "She may not show it, but she is really upset over your father. She loves him and misses him too. "
    sp "Ela pode não o demonstrar, mas está realmente perturbada com o teu pai. Ela ama-o e sente a falta dele também. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:410
translate portuguese dinner3_856a2ed5:

    # sp "And even though she'd probably never tell you, I know she missed you as well. "
    sp "E mesmo que ela provavelmente nunca te dissesse, sei que sentiu a tua falta também. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:411
translate portuguese dinner3_54567235:

    # sp "She was different after you left. Quieter and sullen. Lonely, I think. "
    sp "Ela ficou diferente depois de teres partido. Mais calada e taciturna. Solitária, acho eu. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:412
translate portuguese dinner3_02d1dafd:

    # sp "I know you two didn't hang out much, but I think she liked that you were always there to have her back. When you left, I think she felt a little abandoned. "
    sp "Sei que vocês duas não se davam muito, mas acho que ela gostava do facto de estares sempre lá para a apoiar. Quando partiste, acho que ela se sentiu um pouco abandonada. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:413
translate portuguese dinner3_2aec8af1:

    # "I never thought about that really. I didn't have a close relationship with Suzy, but we didn't fight really either. I was mad at my dad when I left, and resentful towards Lisa and Suzy for taking him away from me. "
    "Nunca pensei nisso, na verdade. Eu não tinha uma relação próxima com a Suzy, mas também não brigávamos. Eu estava zangada com o meu pai quando parti, e ressentida com a Lisa e a Suzy por o terem tirado de mim. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:414
translate portuguese dinner3_9b39d1de:

    # "I never really gave them a chance. "
    "Nunca lhes dei realmente uma oportunidade. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:415
translate portuguese dinner3_4270ba94:

    # pc "I'm sorry for how I acted before I left. I've done a lot of growing up since then. I shouldn't have treated you and Suzy like I did. "
    pc "Peço desculpa pela forma como agi antes de partir. Amadureci muito desde então. Não devia ter tratado de ti e da Suzy como tratei. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:417
translate portuguese dinner3_f468cec8:

    # sp "Oh, you are beyond forgiven. You were a teenager. I get it. "
    sp "Oh, estás mais do que perdoada. Eras adolescente. Eu entendo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:418
translate portuguese dinner3_e1c5605f:

    # sp "Your dad understood too. He was never upset at you. "
    sp "O teu pai também entendia. Ele nunca ficou chateado contigo. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:419
translate portuguese dinner3_983990a9:

    # pc "I wish he was here. "
    pc "Quem me dera que ele estivesse aqui. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:421
translate portuguese dinner3_b9c6a980:

    # sp "Me too."
    sp "Eu também."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:424
translate portuguese dinner3_f2041521:

    # "I stand up next to her and give her a hug, holding her close. "
    "Levanto-me ao lado dela e dou-lhe um abraço, segurando-a com força. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:426
translate portuguese dinner3_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou2.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_iloveyou2.wav'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:427
translate portuguese dinner3_dbd4b8fb:

    # sp "I love you."
    sp "Amo-te."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:428
translate portuguese dinner3_931fdb2e:

    # pc "I love you too, Lisa."
    pc "Também te amo, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:430
translate portuguese dishes_90fef3a5:

    # pc "I'll get the dishes, okay?"
    pc "Vou lavar a louça, está bem?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:431
translate portuguese dishes_cdac8c69:

    # sp "Oh you don't have to do that. I'll get them."
    sp "Oh, não precisas de fazer isso. Eu trato disso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:432
translate portuguese dishes_8c3d6761:

    # pc "It's okay. You fed me, it's the least I can do."
    pc "Não faz mal. Deste-me de comer, é o mínimo que posso fazer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:435
translate portuguese dishes_631bfdab:

    # "I pick up the empty plates from the table and carry them into the kitchen, setting them into the sink."
    "Pego nos pratos vazios da mesa e levo-os para a cozinha, colocando-os na pia."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:438
translate portuguese dishes_96b0df67:

    # "Then I start washing dishes while she puts what little leftovers there are into storage containers and into the refrigerator."
    "Depois começo a lavar a louça enquanto ela coloca as poucas sobras que restam em recipientes de armazenamento e no frigorífico."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:439
translate portuguese dishes_9d9933cd:

    # sp "You don't have to do all of them, [pcname]. Some of those dishes are from a few days ago."
    sp "Não precisas de lavar tudo, [pcname]. Alguns desses pratos são de há alguns dias."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:440
translate portuguese dishes_e9dbfb00:

    # pc "It's no problem, really. I don't mind."
    pc "Não há problema, a sério. Não me importo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:441
translate portuguese dishes_92402374:

    # "I scrub the dishes and put them away into the dishwasher. She's right. It seems the dishes have been piling in the sink for a few days. It's mostly coffee cups and silverware though."
    "Esfrego os pratos e coloco-os na máquina de lavar louça. Ela tem razão. Parece que os pratos se têm acumulado na pia há alguns dias. Mas são principalmente chávenas de café e talheres."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:442
translate portuguese dishes_e91f1694:

    # "While I do the dishes, Lisa wipes off the counter and the stove, then comes over and stands next to me, watching and smiling."
    "Enquanto lavo a louça, a Lisa limpa a bancada e o fogão, depois aproxima-se e fica ao meu lado, a observar e a sorrir."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:445
translate portuguese dishes_688415e5:

    # sp "It's so great having you back home."
    sp "É tão bom ter-te de volta a casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:446
translate portuguese dishes_8ba74747:

    # sp "And not just to help out with the chores."
    sp "E não é só para ajudar nas tarefas domésticas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:447
translate portuguese dishes_be5f85fa:

    # sp "Look at you. You're all grown up now. You turned out to be such a great person."
    sp "Olha para ti. Já estás crescido. Tornaste-te numa pessoa tão fantástica."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:448
translate portuguese dishes_0621a10e:

    # sp "I'm proud of you, [pcname]."
    sp "Tenho orgulho em ti, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:449
translate portuguese dishes_419a081b:

    # pc "Thanks, Lisa."
    pc "Obrigado, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:450
translate portuguese dishes_2e22a4be:

    # sp "You don't have to call me by my first name, you know."
    sp "Não precisas de me chamar pelo meu primeiro nome, sabes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:451
translate portuguese dishes_49c20c2a:

    # sp "Isn't there something else you'd rather call me?"
    sp "Não há outra coisa com que preferisses chamar-me?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:464
translate portuguese dishes_255098d6:

    # pc "I guess I could call you [mom]."
    pc "Acho que te poderia chamar [mom]."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:465
translate portuguese dishes_fe663261:

    # "She smiles and rubs my back with one hand."
    "Ela sorri e esfrega-me as costas com uma mão."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:466
translate portuguese dishes_74fbfcd0:

    # sp "I like that."
    sp "Gosto disso."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:469
translate portuguese notreadymom_1d99098b:

    # sp "I understand, but I hope you will be some day."
    sp "Eu entendo, mas espero que um dia o sejas."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:474
translate portuguese dishesdone_e3f22ce7:

    # "It only takes about ten minutes to finish the dishes, then I start the dishwasher and dry off my hands."
    "Demora apenas cerca de dez minutos a terminar a louça, depois ligo a máquina de lavar louça e seco as mãos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:477
translate portuguese dishesdone_0600f8f0:

    # sp "Thank you so much for the help."
    sp "Muito obrigada pela ajuda."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:478
translate portuguese dishesdone_aaa5ef92:

    # pc "It's no problem at all. I'll try to help you more around the house too."
    pc "Não há problema nenhum. Vou tentar ajudar-te mais nas tarefas domésticas também."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:479
translate portuguese dishesdone_6d09b2a0:

    # sp "I could definitely use it. Between looking for your father and having to work all the time, I just don't seem to have enough time in the day."
    sp "Preciso mesmo disso. Entre procurar o teu pai e ter de trabalhar o tempo todo, parece que não tenho tempo suficiente no dia."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:482
translate portuguese bedtime_108b39c6:

    # pc "I'm getting pretty tired. I should probably go get ready for bed. It sounds like I have a big day tomorrow."
    pc "Estou a ficar bastante cansada. Provavelmente devia ir preparar-me para dormir. Parece que amanhã vou ter um dia importante."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:483
translate portuguese bedtime_35fcb529:

    # sp "Oh you're right, it is getting late."
    sp "Ah, tens razão, está a ficar tarde."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:484
translate portuguese bedtime_37eafefd:

    # sp "Your bed should be made up, but let me know if you need anything else."
    sp "A tua cama deve estar feita, mas avisa-me se precisares de mais alguma coisa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:485
translate portuguese bedtime_34bcfe10:

    # pc "I should be good. Thanks. "
    pc "Devo ficar bem. Obrigado. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:486
translate portuguese bedtime_39e280b3:

    # sp "You're welcome. Goodnight honey. "
    sp "De nada. Boa noite, querido. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:490
translate portuguese bedtime_cb73fb79:

    # "I start walking up the stairs, but stop when she calls up after me."
    "Começo a subir as escadas, mas paro quando ela me chama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:491
translate portuguese bedtime_d7236e30:

    # sp "Hey."
    sp "Ei."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:493
translate portuguese bedtime_ac8e7326:

    # sp "I'm so glad you're home. "
    sp "Estou tão feliz por estares em casa. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:494
translate portuguese bedtime_0e1f6f09:

    # pc "I'm glad to be home. "
    pc "Estou feliz por estar em casa. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:495
translate portuguese bedtime_c2eac4d5:

    # "And surprisingly, that is true. I had been nervous the entire way here, but now it is starting to feel like home again. I've missed this place and these people. "
    "E, surpreendentemente, isso é verdade. Estive nervoso durante todo o caminho até aqui, mas agora começo a sentir-me em casa novamente. Tive saudades deste lugar e destas pessoas. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:496
translate portuguese bedtime_8988551c:

    # "And I am excited to get my life started again. "
    "E estou entusiasmado por recomeçar a minha vida. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:499
translate portuguese bedtime_a9cb4b72:

    # "I walk up and go into my bedroom, closing the door behind me."
    "Subo as escadas e entro no meu quarto, fechando a porta atrás de mim."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:502
translate portuguese bedtime_34780e18:

    # "I can't help but think of all the things that I need to do."
    "Não consigo deixar de pensar em todas as coisas que preciso de fazer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:503
translate portuguese bedtime_78eef5f3:

    # "Register for college, find a job, get a car, get a phone. "
    "Inscrever-me na faculdade, arranjar um emprego, comprar um carro, arranjar um telemóvel. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:504
translate portuguese bedtime_733bb6e8:

    # "And maybe most important of all, I need to find out what happened to my dad."
    "E talvez o mais importante de tudo, preciso de descobrir o que aconteceu ao meu pai."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:505
translate portuguese bedtime_dea2a7f7:

    # "Something catches my attention from the corner of my eye. There is a clear view between my window and the window in the house next door. Jamie's window. "
    "Algo chama-me a atenção pelo canto do olho. Há uma vista desimpedida entre a minha janela e a janela da casa ao lado. A janela da Jamie. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:509
translate portuguese bedtime_2b3df239:

    # "Her curtains are open, and I see her moving around in her bedroom."
    "As cortinas dela estão abertas e vejo-a a movimentar-se no quarto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:510
translate portuguese bedtime_d26fe3f6:

    # "She is dressed for bed and dancing a little to some music that I can't hear. "
    "Ela está vestida para dormir e a dançar um pouco ao som de uma música que não consigo ouvir. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:517
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_b1acde04:

    # "I stand there watching. This isn't the first time that this had happened. I remember back when I was a teenager, watching her through this same window."
    "Fico ali a observar. Não é a primeira vez que isto acontece. Lembro-me de quando era adolescente, a observá-la através desta mesma janela."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:518
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_829b69aa:

    # "Sometimes I could catch quite the show."
    "Às vezes, conseguia assistir a um verdadeiro espetáculo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:519
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_f4cd189f:

    # "She dances around a little longer, looking quite nice in her t-shirt and short shorts."
    "Ela dança por mais algum tempo, com um ar muito bonito na sua t-shirt e calções curtos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:522
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_a9d11f9b:

    # "Then she looks right up at me. I am caught!"
    "Depois, olha diretamente para mim. Fui apanhado!"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:523
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_416b1742:

    # "I start to turn around, pretend that I hadn't seen anything. That I hadn't been watching."
    "Começo a virar-me, a fingir que não vi nada. Que não estava a observar."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:526
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_015e93e4:

    # "But she just smiles and waves."
    "Mas ela apenas sorri e acena."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:527
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_4f3a3ee4:

    # "I wave back."
    "Aceno de volta."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:530
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_47c7c917:

    # "Then she walks over to the window and closes the curtain."
    "Depois, ela aproxima-se da janela e fecha a cortina."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:531
translate portuguese keepwatchingjamie0_a0ca000d:

    # "Show's over folks, time to go to bed."
    "O espetáculo acabou, pessoal, está na hora de ir para a cama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:536
translate portuguese stopwatchingjamie0_9d8f3e71:

    # "I shouldn't be watching. That's a pretty creepy thing to do."
    "Não devia estar a observar. É uma coisa bastante assustadora de se fazer."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:537
translate portuguese stopwatchingjamie0_157d17b0:

    # "I turn away and try not to think about what I might be missing."
    "Desvio o olhar e tento não pensar no que posso estar a perder."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:540
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_e8de2125:

    # "I take my toothbrush from my suitcase and open the door that leads into the bathroom between Suzy's room and my room."
    "Pego na minha escova de dentes da mala e abro a porta que dá acesso à casa de banho entre o quarto da Suzy e o meu."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:543
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_758405dc:

    # "The door that leads into her bedroom is open and I see her lying on the bed in her night clothes, talking into her cell phone. "
    "A porta que dá acesso ao quarto dela está aberta e vejo-a deitada na cama, de pijama, a falar ao telemóvel. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:545
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_d1f1872b:

    # "She gives me an annoyed look."
    "Ela lança-me um olhar irritado."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:547
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_day0_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_day0_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:548
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_9fef9570:

    # ss "Ugh! Are you going to shut the door or just stand there staring at me like a pervert?"
    ss "Ugh! Vais fechar a porta ou vais ficar aí parado a olhar para mim como um pervertido?"

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:549
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_b2395364:

    # pc "Sorry."
    pc "Desculpa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:552
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_1698b2b6:

    # "I shut the door quickly, giving both of us our privacy."
    "Fecho a porta rapidamente, dando privacidade a ambos."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:553
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_44d2215b:

    # "This is going to take some getting used to."
    "Vou ter de me habituar a isto."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:554
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_3e0e7e7e:

    # "I turn to the sink. It is all covered with her things."
    "Viro-me para o lavatório. Está todo coberto com as coisas dela."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:555
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_6c8adbe6:

    # "I find the toothpaste among the clutter of hair products and makeup and brush my teeth, then clear out a place for me to keep my toothbrush."
    "Encontro a pasta de dentes no meio da confusão de produtos para o cabelo e maquilhagem e escovo os dentes, depois arrumo um espaço para guardar a minha escova de dentes."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:556
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_ccb610d3:

    # "I've been gone for three years. I hate to just come back and force her to make room for me, but I am going to need some space in here as well if we have to share this bathroom."
    "Estive fora durante três anos. Detesto voltar e obrigá-la a arranjar espaço para mim, mas também vou precisar de algum espaço aqui, se tivermos de partilhar esta casa de banho."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:557
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_fbfe7d80:

    # "With that done, I head to bed."
    "Feito isso, vou para a cama."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:560
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_ce296358:

    # "The bed is soft. Even more so than I remember. And the sheets smell like home."
    "A cama é macia. Ainda mais do que me lembrava. E os lençóis cheiram a casa."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:561
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_ada2c3fb:

    # "All of this just feels so comforting. It is strange. At first, I had been worried that you could never go home again. That this would all be too different, and I wouldn't fit in here anymore. "
    "Tudo isto parece tão reconfortante. É estranho. No início, estava preocupada que nunca mais pudesse voltar para casa. Que tudo isto fosse demasiado diferente e que eu já não me encaixasse aqui. "

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:562
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_639a54c3:

    # "Now though. Now I feel good about all of it. I feel like I am home for the first time in a long time."
    "Mas agora. Agora sinto-me bem com tudo isto. Sinto que estou em casa pela primeira vez em muito tempo."

# game/Scenes/Prologue/day0.rpy:563
translate portuguese getreadyforbed_f4f9d6d2:

    # "Just one thing is missing – Dad."
    "Só falta uma coisa – o pai."

